-to unite the seals beyond light, in the hr, outside of time...aka kill the seal droppers in the temple in a certain time frame spawns the glyphed<br>
-you kill the glyphed which is what is created when the mobs are killed(seals united) in the time frame in the temple which spawns the exiled<br>
-you destroy the exiled who spawns the cursed who shouts he is here to kill your gods<br>
-glyphed, exiled, and cursed have to be killed in a certain amount of time or they will depop<br>
<br>
