<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Why is Lord Seru locked up? Is he with or againts the citizens of Sanctus Seru?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Seru isn't locked up, he's in hibernation.  It's been hundreds of years since the Combine came to Luclin, and the human lifespan is limited.<br>
                             <br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Why is all of Sanctus Seru really weird? Is there something controlling them?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
It's a fascist, totalitarian society ruled by beaurocracy and kept in line with the Question.  What did you expect them to be like?<br>
                             <br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> What is behind that door in Shadowhaven? What great massacre happened there?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Just another unimplemented zone, I expect.<br>
                             <br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> The Deep obviously was a result of something happening, and things were found that shouldnt have been, how did this happen?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
This I don't know.<br>
                             <br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Why cant we get into Vex Thal?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
                             <br>
For the same reason we can't get into Sleeper's Tomb.  The folks who built it don't want mortals running around inside.  Eventually the key quest will be implemented/solved.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Is Luclin trapped in Vex Thal?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
                             <br>
No more than Tunare is trapped in PoG.<br>
                             <br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> How does Greig fit into everything? Why does he have these alternate forms? Why is he locked in there?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
                             <br>
Grieg built the massive spires in Mons Letalis attempting to reestablish the connection to Norrath.  Doing so accidently opened a gateway to the Plane of Shadow, like Paineel did with the Underfoot, but this time there was no Dartain around to seal it back up.  Luclin claimed Grieg as a plaything and drove him insane.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> What is up in Ssra Temple? How much in control are the snakes? Who is this Emporer? How are all the other high level mobs in Ssra tied in with this?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
The Shissar are completely seperate from the other factions.  They fled Norrath when the gods tried to exterminate them, and have been hiding in the Grey ever since.<br>
                             <br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> What do the boss mobs in Akheva have to do with this?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
That's actually an interesting question.  The relationships between Akheva, Luclin and the Order of Autarkic Umbrage aren't very well explained.<br>
                             <br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Are Katta and Sanctus Seru at war? Why?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Seru hates the Kattans because they're amoral powermongers who destroyed the Combine.  The Kattans hate Seru because they're moral powermongers who destroyed the Combine.  Mostly, they both just want to go home at this point.<br>
                             <br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> What is up in Katta? What is up with this Nathyn and Valdanov quest?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
