<br>
Within these seals<br>
Exiled to darkness<br>
Beyond light<br>
Outside of time<br>
Lies a power corrupt<br>
<br>
These unbreakable seals<br>
While united in the hour<br>
If united in destruction<br>
Will return the exiled<br>
The destroyer of the Gods<br>
<br>
Here is a thought.  The text refers to 'these seals'.  Maybe this refers to the seals when they were whole.  While the author thought the seals to be unbreakable, they apparently were not , as they were later shattered into the 10 (or more) fragments that have been found.  So, perhaps they need to be combined in sets to create whole seals.  These seals may be the keys to the locked doors that were found.<br>
<br>
Just something to chew on.<br>
